at the end of it all, Ellie has to do something. Bunny wants to ask Ellie for a favor. Dye the Bunny. Dye the Bunny, Ellie.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377980/extras/00f954dc7e4bdfe45ff1ae8c43b3663f.poster.avif?t=1744745197\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377980/extras/00f954dc7e4bdfe45ff1ae8c43b3663f.webm?t=1744745197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377980/extras/00f954dc7e4bdfe45ff1ae8c43b3663f.mp4?t=1744745197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game also features more endings after the game is completed for further exploration, story and a dark twist.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377980/extras/c80b34ecaceca3d9c3610c415bfd6c06.poster.avif?t=1744745197\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377980/extras/c80b34ecaceca3d9c3610c415bfd6c06.webm?t=1744745197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377980/extras/c80b34ecaceca3d9c3610c415bfd6c06.mp4?t=1744745197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377980/extras/b136c1388210740a38d2bf9c718f7dc8.poster.avif?t=1744745197\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377980/extras/b136c1388210740a38d2bf9c718f7dc8.webm?t=1744745197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_